snippet.title: Cornmaze Craze Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Steam Page: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1739130/Cornmaze_Craze/

The Official Trailer for Cornmaze Craze, releasing October 29! You can wishlist it on steam now!

This is my first commercial game and I worked really hard on it these past few months. Special thanks goes out to FxeKeen and Zephyr Beats, who made the soundtrack, and Kifchris, who made the sound effects!

Devlog coming soon!
